BBQ Blitz - Season 1, Episode 2



Kansas City Showdown

Food Network Star winner Eddie Jackson heads to Kansas City, Mo., home of cool jazz music and, of course, sizzling hot barbecue. The hottest chefs in town will test out their skills and compete for the chance to win $5,000. Chef Jasper Mirabile and former Kansas City Chiefs linebacker Quinton Caver will determine who has the chops to be crowned BBQ Blitz Kansas City Champion!



Original Air Date: 16-Oct-2015
